{"tid":136283,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【美國入境禁令影響】21歲敘利亞攝影師未能入境 無緣出席奧斯卡","createTime":"2017-02-27T03:02:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-28T06:03:00.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"49ac8932c5d19719044753c83fafe161e4a379b7","tid":136283,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T03:02:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170226&amp;guid=56355719&amp;category_guid=7018882&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170226%26guid%3D56355719%26category_guid%3D7018882%26category%3Dinstant&d=%2FPdnyacYoUlJSF57jd07D54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=cff5f8e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170226%26guid%3D56355719%26category_guid%3D7018882%26category%3Dinstant&h=2e1a3650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170226&amp;guid=56355719&amp;category_guid=7018882&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n2017-02-26 12:58:05 HKT  <br />\n         <img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170226/large/1488084923_a78c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170226%2Flarge%2F1488084923_a78c.jpg&h=191f6b87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n21歲敘利亞攝影師 haled Khatib受美國入境禁令影響，無法入境。<br />\n<br />\n《The White Helmets》入圍本屆奧斯卡最佳紀錄短片。<br />\n<br />\n影片記錄戰火對民眾嘅迫害，與救援人員嘅工作。<br />\n第89屆奧斯卡頒獎禮將於香港時間明天早上舉行，今年Now TV嘅HBO頻道（NOW 115台）HBO HD（NOW 110台）以及HBO go應用程式都可以睇到直播。<br />\n<br />\n受到特朗普所頒佈嘅禁止穆斯林國家旅客入境行政命令影響，伊朗導演阿斯加法哈迪（Asghar Farhadi）雖然憑《伊朗式遷居》（The Salesman）角逐最佳外語片，但佢已表明唔會出席於香港時間聽日舉行嘅第89屆奧斯卡頒獎禮。<br />\n<br />\n至於憑《The White Helmets》入圍最佳紀錄短片嘅21歲敘利亞攝影師 Khaled Khatib，同樣因禁令影響未能入境，無緣現身奧斯卡會場。<br />\n<br />\nKhaled Khatib乘搭土耳其航空飛抵當地，但佢噚日於Twitter留言，原先指自己主要任務係幫助敘利亞人民，所以唔會去奧斯卡。數小時後佢再更新Twitter，表明原來佢係無法出席，Khaled Khatib指已申請美國簽證，但留喺機場3日仍未能順利入境。美國國土安全部方面係以查獲關於Khaled Khatib不利情報，而拒絕讓佢入境。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，Greg P. Russell原本與Gary Summers、Jeffrey J Haboush及Mac Ruth，憑《13小時：班加西無名英雄》（13 Hours: The Secret Soldiers of Benghazi）入圍爭奧斯卡最佳音響效果，但Greg P. Russell被指干擾投票過程，於頒獎禮前一日被取消入圍資格，但其餘三位入圍者仍然可以憑《13小時》爭獎。"},{"pid":"b3bc91565324dec146ab49368001060b094f2010","tid":136283,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T03:15:15.000Z","msg":"禁令唔係hold住左咩"},{"pid":"2f6e24b6436be677945932d1cb126b423fb26101","tid":136283,"uid":13678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T03:50:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>禁令唔係hold住左咩</blockquote><br />\n行政命令係即時生效<br />\n推翻命令要靠法院國會等等開會推翻（好似係<br />\n總之而家就生效緊，但依然有官司打緊"},{"pid":"cc945617673d4ea6fcb944efcc78f6388ebd41ff","tid":136283,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T04:39:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bf478162dcfe36c1e8797edb02f9a25bfaa298c","tid":136283,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T04:57:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3d6581660d8c4e62479775148efa7ac71a4edee","tid":136283,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T05:12:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36eec6ce54d948403cab3bee4446cb30efc39d7b","tid":136283,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T06:03:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}